{"tid":1883743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ DSE 2020 ] 5.2萬人報考文憑試創新低　逾百人爭做超級狀元","createTime":"2020-02-17T07:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T07:22:39.000Z","uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a38dc3576d3c48752dd8289d73ad912e63d38411","tid":1883743,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:22:39.000Z","msg":"撰文：杜潔心<br />\n2020-01-20 14:20<br />\n最後更新日期：2020-01-20 18:52<br />\n<br />\n2020年的中學文憑試主科將於3月30日正式開考，隨適齡學童下降影響，考評局今日(20日)公布，今年共有52,687名學生報考文憑試，較去年少3618人，約減少6.4%；亦創自2012年文憑試推行以來新低。<br />\n<br />\n而一直備受關注的中國歷史科，今年則有6079名考生報考，較去年減少逾300人；至於有機會問鼎八科「超級狀元」，報考四個核心科目及四個選修科目的考生則有104人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D9jH7j8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD9jH7j8.png&h=4b7e859b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020 年文憑試主科將於3月30日開始，今年有45,931名學校考生以及6,756名自修生，共52,687人報考。<br />\n<br />\n當中有104人報考四個核心科目及四個選修科目(即「4+4」)，佔考生0.2%；報考三個選修科(「4+3」)，即共7科的有8,562人，佔18.6%；有69.9%考生報考「4+2」，至於「4+1」則有3,662人報考佔8%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/424033/dse-2020-5-2%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E5%A0%B1%E8%80%83%E6%96%87%E6%86%91%E8%A9%A6%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%8E-%E9%80%BE%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%BA%E7%88%AD%E5%81%9A%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E7%8B%80%E5%85%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F424033%2Fdse-2020-5-2%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2586%2591%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25BD%258E-%25E9%2580%25BE%25E7%2599%25BE%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%2581%259A%25E8%25B6%2585%25E7%25B4%259A%25E7%258B%2580%25E5%2585%2583&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=8e17aa24\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/424033/dse-2020-5-2%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E5%A0%B1%E8%80%83%E6%96%87%E6%86%91%E8%A9%A6%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%8E-%E9%80%BE%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%BA%E7%88%AD%E5%81%9A%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E7%8B%80%E5%85%83</a><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n考評局資料<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a4wLkHx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa4wLkHx.jpg&h=3cd46ad0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ubj5kHA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fubj5kHA.jpg&h=67fff939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dyXOiud.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdyXOiud.jpg&h=410e043c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jmPH7nB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjmPH7nB.jpg&h=674dff0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TT58iui.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTT58iui.jpg&h=e46b5444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hHhuNnx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhHhuNnx.jpg&h=c7f86446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/DocLibrary/Media/FactFigures/2020HKDSE_registrationstat.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkeaa.edu.hk%2FDocLibrary%2FMedia%2FFactFigures%2F2020HKDSE_registrationstat.pdf&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=af771ab0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/DocLibrary/Media/FactFigures/2020HKDSE_registrationstat.pdf</a>"}]}